Package gw.cc.aggregatelimit.entity

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AggregateLimit
    AggregateLimit An annual or lifetime aggregate limit on a policy or coverage.
    AggregateLimitRpt
    AggregateLimitRpt An annual or lifetime aggregate limit on a policy or coverage.
    AggregateLimitRptDelegate
    AggregateLimitRptDelegate Common state and behavior shared by both the AggregateLimitRpt and ClaimAggregateLimitRpt entities.
    ClaimAggregateLimitRpt
    ClaimAggregateLimitRpt Represents denormalized aggregate limit used calculations (i.e., the amount of the limit that has been used to date) for a claim as related to a given aggregate limit and optionally, for a coverageline.
    CoverageLine
    CoverageLine An annual or lifetime aggregate limit on a policy or coverage.
    CoverageLineLimit
    CoverageLineLimit Links coverages to aggregate limits.
    PeriodPolicy
    PolicyPeriodPolicy Links a PolicyPeriod with its policies.
    PolicyPeriod
    PolicyPeriod An annual or lifetime aggregate limit on a policy or coverage.
    TmpAggregateLimitOracle
    TmpAggregateLimitOracle Tmp table for populating the aggregate limit denorm table, cc_agglimitrpt.
    TmpAggregateLimitRpt
    TmpAggregateLimitRpt Tmp table for populating the aggregate limit denorm table, cc_agglimitrpt.
    TmpStagingAggregateLimit
    TmpStagingAggregateLimit Temporary table for populating the aggregate limit denorm table, cc_agglimitrpt, from the staging tables.
    TmpStagingAggregateLimit2
    TmpStagingAggregateLimit2 Temporary table for setting rows as invalid in the aggregate limit denorm table, cc_agglimitrpt, from the staging tables.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CoverageLine.CoverageLineConfiguration
    enumeration of allowable coverage line configurations
